  Package   : line_follower
  Team      : VEGA
  Framework : ROS 2 Humble Hawksbill
  Format    : REP-149  (package format 3)
  License   : MIT

  Description:
    Autonomous differential-drive line-following robot using ROS 2 Humble,
    ATmega32 microcontroller, HC-05 Bluetooth UART bridge, 5-element IR
    sensor array, optical wheel encoders, and a PID controller.

